content:
To create swarm reports, use the out-of-the-box Service Cloud Swarming Reports and Dashboards AppExchange package, or create one of three report types. The package preconfigures report types, delivers several Swarming reports, and includes a complete swarming dashboard.

To manually create a Swarming report, choose from:

* Case report type: uses Swarm Member as a secondary relationship
* Swarm Member report type: uses Swarm Member as the primary relationship
* Swarm report type: uses Swarm as the primary relationship

From Setup, enter Reports and Dashboards, select Report Types, select a report type, assign a secondary relationship, and save changes.
title: Swarm Report Creation in Service Cloud
